{"word":"ὁδοποιός","slug":"ὁδοποιός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὁδοποιός</b></el> <el>(ὁδο-ποιός, οῦ, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ποιέω'><el>ποιέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>one who opens the way, a pioneer</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a road-surveyor</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}